title: Couple With Heart Man Man Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic couple composed of two men, with both men having a medium-dark skin tone. It signifies love, partnership, and gay relationships.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the couple with a heart emoji, featuring two men with medium-dark skin tones, radiates a sense of devoted connection. The glossy red heart between them pops with Apple's characteristic 3D sheen, symbolizing strong affection and commitment.  The men's figures are rendered with soft, rounded edges and naturalistic lighting, conveying warmth and unity in their relationship, ideal for expressing love and partnership.
